{"tid":800881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[6月29]建造業對人才需求大，年輕人要好好裝備自己，把握機遇","createTime":"2018-08-31T08:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T14:26:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"00403bf80c96114299937f78309fdb6c6b5462de","tid":800881,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:14:15.000Z","msg":"建造業對人才需求大，業界<span style=\"color: red;\">年輕人要好好裝備自己，把握機遇</span>，參加技能比賽是其中一個好方法。香港建造業議會（下稱「議會」）日前舉辦「香港建造業青年技能大賽」，設砌磚、細木等6個比賽項目，由行內「老行尊」擔任評審。參賽者都凝神屏氣，在各個項目一較高下，當中最年輕的參賽者只有16歲，更勇奪項目冠軍，令人驚喜！<br />\n<br />\n議會執行總監鄭定寕指，<span style=\"color: red;\">不少年輕人有感建造業發展前景良好，有意加入</span>，未來議會將提供更多培訓課程，及舉辦更多活動提升他們的專業技能。有經驗的師傅則可傳授工藝予年輕人，驅使建造業逐步邁向專業化和科技化，為建造業增添新血。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180629/photo/bkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180629083334\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180629083334&h=6471a74a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180629/bkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180629%2Fbkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001.html&d=0%2F%2Bsm2iTreXJo34rCNGgVv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=92a56112\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180629/bkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b2739681212ad0dee7b14a24b9f927904c044839","tid":800881,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:14:47.000Z","msg":"★14工人追禮頓63萬欠薪　官驚嘆日薪$900非巿價<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/800787\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/800787</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1c7a0e298eab9f3e7269353f2b06ee649963d2a5","tid":800881,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b2739681212ad0dee7b14a24b9f927904c044839","tid":800881,"uid":19454,"li